  "conditionals": 57,
  "created": "2025-10-15",
  "description": "The Unfolded Protein Response (UPR) in S. cerevisiae responds to ER stress caused by accumulation of misfolded proteins. The sensor Ire1 is an ER transmembrane kinase-endoribonuclease that oligomerizes upon binding unfolded proteins in the ER lumen. Activated Ire1 splices HAC1 mRNA, removing an intron to produce functional Hac1 transcription factor. Hac1 enters the nucleus and activates UPR target genes encoding ER chaperones, ERAD components, and lipid biosynthesis enzymes to expand ER capacity.",
  "id": "yeast_er_stress_response",
  "keywords": [
    "UPR",
    "ER stress",
    "Ire1",
    "Hac1",
    "unfolded protein response"
  ],
  "lastUpdated": "2025-10-15",
  "logicGates": {
    "and": 5,
    "not": 3,
    "or": 3
  },
  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    %% ER Stress Triggers\n    A[Protein Synthesis Increase] --> B[ER Protein Load]\n    C[Mutations in Proteins] --> D[Misfolded Proteins]\n    E[Calcium Depletion] --> F[Chaperone Dysfunction]\n    G[Reducing Agents DTT] --> H[Disulfide Bond Disruption]\n    I[Tunicamycin Treatment] --> J[/Glycosylation Block/]\n    \n    %% OR Gate 1: ER Stress Detection\n    B --> K{OR: Unfolded<br/>Proteins in ER?}\n    D --> K\n    F --> K\n    H --> K\n    J --> K\n    K -->|No| L[Normal ER Homeostasis]\n    K -->|Yes| M[ER Stress Condition]\n    \n    %% Ire1 Sensing\n    M --> N[Ire1 Binds Unfolded Proteins]\n    N --> O[Ire1 Oligomerization]\n    \n    %% AND Gate 1: Ire1 Trans-autophosphorylation\n    O --> P{AND: Ire1 Dimers<br/>Formed?}\n    P -->|No - Monomers| L\n    P -->|Yes - Oligomers| Q[Ire1 Trans-autophosphorylation]\n    \n    Q --> R[Ire1 Kinase Domain Active]\n    R --> S[Ire1 RNase Domain Activated]\n    \n    %% HAC1 mRNA Splicing\n    S --> T[Constitutive HAC1u mRNA]\n    T --> U[Ire1 Recognizes Stem-Loops]\n    \n    %% AND Gate 2: Both Splice Sites\n    U --> V{AND: 5' Site<br/>AND 3' Site?}\n    V -->|No| W[No Splicing]\n    V -->|Yes| X[Ire1 Cleaves Both Sites]\n    \n    X --> Y[Intron Released]\n    Y --> Z[Exon Ligation]\n    \n    %% AND Gate 3: tRNA Ligase Required\n    Z --> AA{AND: Rlg1/Trl1<br/>Ligase Present?}\n    AA -->|No| AB[Splicing Incomplete]\n    AA -->|Yes| AC[HAC1i mRNA Formed]\n    \n    %% Translation Difference\n    W --> AD[HAC1u has Intron]\n    AD --> AE[Translation Stalled]\n    AE --> AF[No Hac1 Protein]\n    \n    AC --> AG[HAC1i mRNA Translated]\n    AG --> AH[Hac1 Protein Produced]\n    AH --> AI[Hac1 Homodimerization]\n    \n    %% Nuclear Localization\n    AI --> AJ{AND: NLS<br/>Functional?}\n    AJ -->|No| AK[Cytoplasmic Retention]\n    AJ -->|Yes| AL[Hac1 Nuclear Import]\n    \n    AL --> AM[Hac1 DNA Binding]\n    AM --> AN[UPRE Element Recognition]\n    AN --> AO[UPR Target Gene Transcription]\n    \n    %% OR Gate 2: Which UPR Target?\n    AO --> AP{OR: Which Gene<br/>Class?}\n    AP -->|Chaperones| AQ[KAR2 PDI1 Expression]\n    AP -->|ERAD| AR[DER1 HRD1 Expression]\n    AP -->|Lipid Synthesis| AS[INO1 OPI3 Expression]\n    AP -->|Quality Control| AT[EUG1 SCJ1 Expression]\n    \n    %% Chaperone Upregulation\n    AQ --> AU[Kar2/BiP Production]\n    AU --> AV[Pdi1 Disulfide Isomerase]\n    AV --> AW[Enhanced Folding Capacity]\n    \n    %% ERAD Enhancement\n    AR --> AX[Der1 Rhomboid Pseudoprotease]\n    AX --> AY[Hrd1 E3 Ubiquitin Ligase]\n    AY --> AZ[ERAD Complex Assembly]\n    AZ --> BA[/Misfolded Protein Degradation/]\n    \n    %% ER Expansion\n    AS --> BB[Phospholipid Synthesis]\n    BB --> BC[ER Membrane Expansion]\n    BC --> BD[Increased ER Volume]\n    \n    %% AND Gate 4: Resolution Check\n    AW --> BE{AND: Folding Improved<br/>AND ERAD Active?}\n    BA --> BE\n    BE -->|No| BF[Sustained UPR]\n    BE -->|Yes| BG[ER Stress Resolution]\n    \n    %% Feedback Inhibition\n    BG --> BH[Unfolded Proteins Cleared]\n    BH --> BI[Ire1 Deactivation]\n    BI --> BJ[No HAC1 Splicing]\n    BJ --> BK[Hac1 Protein Decay]\n    BK --> BL[/(UPR Termination)/]\n    \n    L --> BM([No UPR Needed])\n    AF --> BM\n    BF --> BN[Chronic ER Stress]\n    BN --> BO{OR: Apoptosis<br/>Pathway?}\n    BO -->|Yes| BP([Cell Death])\n    BO -->|No| BF\n    \n    %% Normal Resolution\n    BD --> BG\n    \n    %% Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style G fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style H fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style I fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style J fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style L fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style M fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style N fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style O fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style P fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style Q fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style R fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style S fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style T fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style U fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style V fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style W fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style X fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Y fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Z fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AA fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AB fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style AC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AD fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AE fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AF fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style AG fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AH fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style AI fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AJ fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AK fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AL fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AM fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AN fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AO fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AP fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style AQ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AR fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AS fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AT fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AU fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style AV fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AW fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AX fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AY fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AZ fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BA fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style BB fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BD fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BE fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style BF fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BG fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style BH fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style BI fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style BJ fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BK fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style BL fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff\n    style BM fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style BN fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style BO fill:#ffd600,color:#fff\n    style BP fill:#000000,color:#fff",
